1. Use a spatial light modulator (SLM) to shape two time-delayed femtosecond pump pulses with different fixed OAM (e.g., \(\ell = +1\) and \(\ell = +3\)).
2. Overlap them to create a hybrid pump whose effective OAM ramps smoothly over ~10 fs.
